Hill:
Intermittent social runners
Benefit from targeted internal data and external data
In order to assess and enhance race performance in an engaging manner.

SubHill:
RAM platform will also give suggestions based on the data analytics and runner preferences, about training programs and other ways to prepare better and perform better in future races.

Story:
As an intermittent social runner
I want to know about RAM races that match my personalized data
So that I participate in the right races in order to enjoy more and/or improve my performance

Acceptance Criteria:
Given I'm an intermittent social runner with RAM account
When I agree to share my running perfprmance with RAM by RAM application
Then I will receive the analysis report from RAM
